Overview
Captain Guido ($GUIDO) is an ERC-20 token deployed on the Ethereum network, designed to mobilize
capital, community, and culture in support of ocean conservation. The project blends blockchain
transparency with structured environmental funding, positioning $GUIDO at the intersection of web3
infrastructure, impact finance, and narrative-driven brand building.
$GUIDO is built to appeal to long-term holders and institutional participants by emphasizing clear token
mechanics, verifiable treasury flows, and disciplined growth rather than short-term speculation.

