Treasury & Environmental Funding Mechanism
Treasury Contribution
A 0.1% contribution is applied to all token sales. Funds collected through this mechanism are routed
automatically to the $GUIDO treasury.
Monthly Treasury Split
Treasury funds are distributed on a recurring monthly basis as follows:
50% allocated to project operations, including development, audits, infrastructure, partnerships, and
compliance
50% donated to verified 501(c)(3) nonprofit organizations focused on ocean conservation
All treasury inflows and outflows are recorded on-chain, with monthly transparency reports published for
token holders and partners.

