Deflationary Mechanics
$GUIDO incorporates a structured burn framework designed to reduce circulating supply over time. Token
burns may occur through:
Unclaimed presale allocations
Designated protocol burn events
All burns are executed on-chain and permanently remove tokens from circulation, reinforcing long-term
scarcity and supply discipline.

Governance Evolution
Captain Guido is initially stewarded by a core foundation to ensure regulatory compliance, execution
efficiency, and capital discipline.
As the ecosystem matures, governance will progressively evolve toward community participation through: -
Non-binding signaling votes - Treasury allocation proposals - Long-term transition to formal DAO-based
governance mechanisms

