Captain Guido Lore (Brand Narrative)
Captain Guido is the symbolic guardian of the world’s oceans—an enduring figure representing
accountability, stewardship, and resistance against environmental degradation. Rather than functioning as
fiction alone, Captain Guido serves as the narrative anchor for the project’s mission: transforming
decentralized capital into measurable environmental action.
The Captain Guido identity reinforces the project’s values of transparency, responsibility, and long-term
thinking—principles that guide treasury decisions, partnerships, and community engagement.

