Conclusion
Captain Guido ($GUIDO) is designed as a disciplined, impact-oriented digital asset with transparent
mechanics and a scalable funding model for ocean conservation. By combining structured tokenomics with
verifiable charitable flows and a strong brand identity, $GUIDO aims to offer long-term value to investors
while delivering measurable real-world impact.
